,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T07:32:54.000Z","msg":"二千二百億成交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f751b095ee61e0b761a05310bd5d0dde9985e595","tid":552012,"uid":152846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T08:54:55.000Z","msg":"大家準備入貨 信神燈 不死"},{"pid":"45db3c53fe58b7dfdc818d74a136475966a5e958","tid":552012,"uid":153407,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T12:15:14.000Z","msg":"入市信號明確"},{"pid":"c4ce2514fe72e1d28a1d6d8ac483459034d48347","tid":552012,"uid":48762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T13:27:05.000Z","msg":"大師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79ea18b472ee18982b6862a60f3d7e2a02ca7e1a","tid":552012,"uid":152846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45db3c53fe58b7dfdc818d74a136475966a5e958","tid":552012,"uid":153407,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T12:15:14.000Z","msg":"入市信號明確"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T02:11:17.000Z","msg":"吊原來係琴日講就要琴日買 即時顯靈"},{"pid":"66574545253bb41ad86b19149332fa0e334dbc28","tid":552012,"uid":146611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T03:11:44.000Z","msg":"乜7都比大師講曬<br />\n<br />\n又話過年前安全，結果跌到碌鳩甘<br />\n<br />\n宜家話月底前破30000"}]}